description:
Name: Nils Holgersson au pays des oies sauvage
Year: 1980
Type: 52-episode TV series, about 23 mins/episode
Style: Animation::Anime
Language: French (dubbed)
Ripped by: Saxoman [tvu.org.ru]
Format: DivX, 496x352

Originally \"Nils no Fushigi na Tabi,\" based on \"Nils Holgerssons underbara resa genom Sverige\" by Selma Lagerlof.  Go to http://www.animenewsnetwork.com/encyclopedia/anime.php?id=1417 or Wikipedia for more info.

So far, I haven\&#039;t found subs for this, so you\&#039;re stuck with the French, which may or may not be problematic.  Shouldn\&#039;t be too bad - the story can be understood moderately well without any dialogue.  It was dubbed into many other languages (I grew up with the Afrikaans version) but the only other ones I\&#039;ve seen on P2P are Arabic (torrent) and German (from tvu.org.ru).

This was not ripped by me.  Credit goes to Saxoman.  I just downloaded it from eMule (was a bit of a pain), and thought it\&#039;d be nice for this to be on BitTorrent.
